dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures and soundings. Includes insets: Baye Matavai, dans O-Taïti -- Plan des havres, situés au côté nord d'Eimeo -- Carte des Marquises de Mendoce. In upper left corner: Cook 1er. voyage. In upper right corner: 125. Probably issued in: Atlas encyclopédique / R. Bonne and N. Desmaret. A Paris : Hôtel de Thou, 1787-1788.
